# Rule Injector shared rules
#
# This file is consumed by:
# - A_inject-rules-proxy.sgmodule -> Proxy
# - B_inject-rules-PROXY.sgmodule -> PROXY
#
# Keep policy names out of this file. The module decides the target policy.
# NOTE: PROCESS-NAME 不能放进外部 RULE-SET，会报错；进程规则放在各模块的 [Rule] 段。

