DOMAIN-SUFFIX,fanbox.cc
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pixiv.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pximg.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gamemale.com
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,kemono
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,pawchive
